songs.title: Money (That’s What I Want)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
The best things in life are free
But you can't give them to the birds and bees
I want money
That's what I want
That's what I want
That's what I want

[Verse 2]
Your love gives me such a thrill
But your love won't pay my bills
I want money
That's what I want
That's what I want
That's what I want
Oh

[Verse 3]
And money don't get everything, it's true
What it don't get, I can't use
I want that money
That's what I want
That's what I want
That's what I want

[Outro]
I want money
I want lots of money
In fact, I want so much money
Give me that money
Get, get, get, get me money
Get, get, get, get me money
I want that money
